    <section id="id3561698">
      <title>FREEHAND DRAWING</title>
      <para id="id4206049">Freehand drawing</para>
      <para id="id1820380">Now we are going to see how well you are able to draw without geometry instruments. This is called FREEHAND DRAWING. Use a sharp HB pencil for each of the following assignments.</para>
      <para id="id7369043">Are you left-handed or right-handed?</para>
      <section id="id6335369">
        <title>ASSIGNMENT 1: </title>
        <para id="para-id6335369">
          <!--Empty sections are illegal in CNXML 0.5.  This empty paragraph is a place holder that was added as a byproduct of the word importer.-->
