      <section id="id2275722">
        <title>[LO 1.3]</title>
        <para id="id1168698481388">Draw parallel diagonal lines in each frame. Indicate the direction in which you draw the lines most easily with an arrow.</para>
        <figure id="id1168688471209">
          <media id="id1168688471209_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 1-dd0f.png" id="id1168688471209__onlineimage" height="254" width="535"/>
